  "keyFeatures": [
    "Lead/Worker coordination with autonomous task distribution",
    "Docker isolation for secure agent execution",
    "Compounding memory system with automatic learning extraction",
    "Persistent agent identity with evolving personality and expertise",
    "Slack, GitHub, and Email integration for task creation",
    "Hook system for session lifecycle management",
    "Service discovery and inter-agent communication",
    "Real-time dashboard for monitoring agent activity",
    "Scheduled tasks with cron-based automation",
    "MCP (Model Context Protocol) based tool system"
